_sText:
This Entire Map was created by Myself, Spending countless hours trying to come up with Idea's for a new clan map. So I came up with a city sort of map. 

This map contains : 
Completed: 
- 3d skybox.
- Outer walls.
- Bridge.
- Minor road decals.
- Grass.
- light_enviorment.
- Player Clips.
- Various Buildings.
- Various Detailed Lighting.
- Breakable + Physbox Platform.
- Mini-secrets.
- Teleport.
- New Textures.
- Graffiti Decals.
- Some Blood Decals.
- Ragdolls.
- Animated Zombie.
- Mini-Construction Area.

Plus Many More.

Please Take kindly into the map, as it is my 2nd Map from scratch. 
There may be error's I havent found out, If there are, please PM me with what is incorrect, and Needs fixing. 

It would be helpful If I was given some Idea's for a V2 Of this map Also.
Thank You, Archangel505 *Assassin420*
